column5: Does anybody know where somebody could get a map for this lakeThanks
are you talking paper map or digital map for a sonar?

As far as digital good luck the provincial gov. is soo uptight about royalties for a mapped lake that we will never likely see a navionics chip in my lifetime. For paper you could try.http://www.fishingmapsplus.com/manit...hazonesj-s.htm

But bring your chest waders, water level was so high that the docks couldn't be put in the water, and with snow levels in-addition to Sask draining lake overflow into the lake we are looking at some flooding this year I can only hope I am not jigging for pics off of my roof
